parameters: \SE[13]Hmph...! This is what happens when you go against us!

\SE[14]There is no value in powerless justice!! But well,
\SE[21]this is harsh...

\SE[13] (Hmm... I wonder if there's any way to deal with the hot-
bloodedness of these women...)

\SE[37] (I wonder if I should consult about this. But there's no
one to talk to...)

Sergeant: I never thought I would have to resort to my secret
weapon! You better regret angering the adults...!!
\SE[2]Oh my...? This is an unexpected development.

Sergeant: With your attack power, you will never be able to break
through the armor of the Titan!! Losing here means it's the end
for you!!

\SE[14]Haa...!? \SE[12]Don't get all cocky just because you
brought out that scrap metal!!

\SE[12]If it's come to this...!! I'll defeat this guy and lighten
the burden on the main force! \SE[14]Everyone, let's go...!!

\SE[14]W-What... W-What are we going to do!? \SE[12]Our attacks
aren't getting through at all...!! \SE[29]Come on, don't we have
some kind of leader or something!?

\SE[12]They always treat me like a leader in times like this!!
\!\SE[13]But, I do need to figure something out...!

\SE[33] (It's not good to be held back here. \!\SE[3] If we take
too much time...)
\SE[12]As I thought, it turned out like this...

\SE[14]I-I can't afford to lose like this! \SE[27]No way! To be
ensnared by these guys...!!

Sergeant: This is what happens when you're so arrogant...! I'll
thoroughly train you so that you'll never dare to speak
disrespectfully again...!! Especially you, little red one!!
Especially you!!

\SE[11]Huh!? Why you! \SE[29]You, you lolicon!!! The worst...!!
Don't come near me!

Sergeant: This...!! \!Take them down!! \.Capture these damn
brats!!

\SE[14]Hey, Laura!? \SE[11]Why are you here...!? \SE[14]This is
supposed to be our responsibility, right!?
Sergeant: Wh-Who are you...? What are you!?
